data.description: Honey, stop the car! This is the one! This beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 Bathroom home located on a cul-de-sac in the highly sought after neighborhood of Hampshire Glen. Super convenient to local military bases, shopping, restaurants, and attractions. This home features an open floor plan, a huge master bedroom with 2 walk-in closets, a covered front porch, a large back patio, and a huge and fully fenced in backyard.  A must see! Did I mention the huge Backyard!! Make this house your home today!
